# GUI Development Rules

Expose `src` codebase features to non-technical users via a simple interface.

## Frontend
- Keep UI clear and minimal.
- Use minimal HTML/CSS; store CSS in the correct file (default: `styles.css`).
  
## Backend / API
- API coordinates only high-level logic from `src`.
- Favor simplicity.
- Follow standard Flask setup.
